<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08032h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08032h">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08032h"> 32(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> sentenced in absentia</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Russian Mock Trial</b> A message from Simferopol states that Bolsheviks recently held a crowded meeting in the theatre there, at which was performed <mark>a mock trial</mark> of Vorowski&apos;s assailants. / Some of the ablest lawyers took part, and <mark>the sentence was</mark> that Conradi and Plunin should be shot and Lord Curzon placed in an internment camp &mdash; until a Labour revolution takes place in Great Britain. <small> <a name="FJ29dec23" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ29dec23"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (29 December 1923) 5/3</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
